{"tid":726515,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★鼓勵淘寶？四電一腦除舊下月實施 需交每件15至165港元的循環再造費。","createTime":"2018-07-02T12:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T12:13:56.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"03f829cdba086b5ec682fa9b1d3f0c840678de03","tid":726515,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T12:44:24.000Z","msg":"廢電器電子產品生產者責任計劃將由8月1日起生效，屆時市民購買俗稱「四電一腦」的產品，可向銷售商要求安排免費除舊服務，而銷售商指定的回收商會為市民移走一件屬相同類別的電器，並送交指定的循環再造商處理。供應商則必須向環境保護署登記，並繳交每件15至165港元的循環再造徵費。<br />\n<br />\n環保署今日(2日)指，四電一腦產品，即空調機、雪櫃、洗衣機、電視機、電腦、打印機、掃描器及顯示器的供應商必須經登記後，才可分發以上的電器。而銷售商必須備有經該署批註的除舊服務方案，才可銷售受管制電器。該署提醒仍未提出申請的業界人士應盡早行動，以確保屆時符合法例要求。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180702/bkn-20180702171438997-0702_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180702%2Fbkn-20180702171438997-0702_00822_001.html&d=RmGgjlo2L4VoqaZYwsVXV7r9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=24c82bbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180702/bkn-20180702171438997-0702_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"88eaf70c53f1f91cfdf4d973d5f1829ad1cdbdc7","tid":726515,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T12:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"007359b7a3b94567cc0b284343afde148a2462a1","tid":726515,"uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T12:45:53.000Z","msg":"香港腦場執得<br />\n<br />\nhk no IT不是夢"},{"pid":"a0759216274731fd5c27dbd42c7834c1e849a99a","tid":726515,"uid":51066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"007359b7a3b94567cc0b284343afde148a2462a1","tid":726515,"uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T12:45:53.000Z","msg":"香港腦場執得<br />\n<br />\nhk no IT不是夢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T12:49:04.000Z","msg":"轉移去消費者之嘛"},{"pid":"c013cb90625bd658ef29909fba1eaba2b2427327","tid":726515,"uid":19454,"like